Package: econocharts
Title: Microeconomics and Macroeconomics Charts Made with 'ggplot2'
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("José Carlos", "Soage González", email = "jsoage@uvigo.es", role = c("aut", "cre")),
   person("Andrew", "Heiss", email = "andrewheiss@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Contains several functions for creating fully-customizable microeconomics or macroeconomics charts, such as supply and demand curves, indifference curves, production-possibility frontiers or Laffer curves.
Imports: ggplot2, dplyr, Hmisc, scales, glue
